 />\n<br />\n之後逃走到，不過個人意識唔太好，再加上慌不擇路，一心只係諗住走而無法睇環境失足。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點都好，popo就算唔係直接，都一L定間接害死周同學。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，今晚八點，為佢默哀。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:16:36.000Z","msg":"佢哋係間接害死周同學，30分鐘可能救返到一條人命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:47:41.000Z","msg":"呢個係事實 吟詩都吟唔甩 同721一樣"},{"pid":"354615f94c5c2521a5d6e9a35686bef4231734bb","tid":1699671,"uid":9412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:47:49.000Z","msg":"傾就唔好講到fc咗咁啦"},{"pid":"1610e4a0d3cf4e83cc07fb676dc01ac2de57aff2","tid":1699671,"uid":21260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:47:54.000Z","msg":"我估計你老母比狗屌呀估計"},{"pid":"0bf71cd28277e54f81a84628a6693616e2056249","tid":1699671,"uid":128157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:48:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"709bc00bbb615b6cafa0e110ead7af2cb9662e61","tid":1699671,"uid":33036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:49:41.000Z","msg":"收皮啦"},{"pid":"0307384fba7c2de4ddf041193ac1e77175b9d63e","tid":1699671,"uid":204031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:50:04.000Z","msg":"屌那星，鳩估就唔好用個咁既標題啦"},{"pid":"e58e57edeecb5347b2f2210f6a5dad2f6b23dd32","tid":1699671,"uid":77158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:50:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e0e03843957936d6c33004002a0641e73ba4d525","tid":1699671,"uid":150907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc9ba136a9dff6ad44e30712c8e8e9b